def is_fryingpan_ready_for_scrambling(fryingpan:item):
    symbol is_ready=exists egg: item : is_food_egg(egg) and on(egg, fryingpan) and not cut(egg)
    return is_ready

behavior crack_egg_onto_fryingpan(fryingpan:item, egg:item):
    body:
        achieve on(egg, fryingpan) # Ensure egg is placed on fryingpan
        achieve cut(egg) # Crack the egg onto the fryingpan

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind fryingpan: item where:
            is_fryingpan(fryingpan)
        # Select the fryingpan

        bind egg: item where:
            is_food_egg(egg) and on(egg, fryingpan)
        # Select the egg on the fryingpan

        if is_fryingpan_ready_for_scrambling(fryingpan):
            crack_egg_onto_fryingpan(fryingpan, egg)
        else:
            observe(fryingpan, "Check if the egg is on and cracked into the frying pan")
